  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/d01412361f73bd1beda5754bf133e54d.avif?t=1745458035\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.poster.avif?t=1745458035\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.webm?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.mp4?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Descend into an intense world of chaotic mining and platforming in <i><strong>Fool's End</strong></i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose to fight your way out with a pickaxe, or use your wits to manipulate the environment and create your own exit. Escape each level in your own way. Everything is destructible....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.poster.avif?t=1745458035\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.webm?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.mp4?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the Fool, a degenerate on a desperate mission to navigate his way out of a tangled system of caves. Dig through and manipulate environmental hazards, evade powerful monsters, smack enemies into lava and bombs, and prepare for an adventure in a land of chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/692f598e5afa9dbf461784d1db991d94.avif?t=1745458035\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your way through fully destructible tile-based terrain.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-risk</strong> quickfire gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 35 hand-crafted <strong>replayable </strong>levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Editor</strong> so you can make and play your own levels.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New <strong>Daily Challenge levels</strong> to play every day.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for a place on top of the Daily Leaderboard.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quirky unique enemies with dramatic <strong>boss fights</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time trials unlocked after finishing each biome.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bumping dynamic <strong>original soundtrack</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret sauce and beverages.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/b3dc8850d85dec38cf8bb953a03e2882.avif?t=1745458035\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/00e65fa1018713adeed812264480b3f6.poster.avif?t=1745458035\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/00e65fa1018713adeed812264480b3f6.webm?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/00e65fa1018713adeed812264480b3f6.mp4?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fool's End includes an original soundtrack with 16 tracks composed by Chris MacClure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1e9058413034f0f848f88a4c99011fdd.avif?t=1745458035\" width=616 height=676 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/d01412361f73bd1beda5754bf133e54d.avif?t=1745458035\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.poster.avif?t=1745458035\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.webm?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/1c66b4290ceffc74a96a8f3d4cb57820.mp4?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Descend into an intense world of chaotic mining and platforming in <i><strong>Fool's End</strong></i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose to fight your way out with a pickaxe, or use your wits to manipulate the environment and create your own exit. Escape each level in your own way. Everything is destructible....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.poster.avif?t=1745458035\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.webm?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636260/extras/878ec7fcb12371951f4098ccb5aab94f.mp4?t=1745458035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the Fool, a degenerate on a desperate